    "content": "nullExperience Cloud\nTABLE OF CONTENTS\nClose\nClose\nSearch\nSearch\n Experience Cloud\n Understand the Basics\n Plan & Prepare\n Set Up & Configure\n Manage Users and Data Access\n Build & Customize\n Create Use-Case Driven Sites\n Secure Your Site\n Test & Deploy\n Manage & Moderate\n Managers, Moderators, and Admins Working Together\n Experience Cloud Site Moderation Strategies and Tools\n Organize Experience Cloud Sites with Topics\n Customize Recommendations in Experience Cloud Sites\n Gamification\n Recognition Badges\n Recognition Badges Limitations\n Recognition Badges Setup\n Missions\n Create a Mission\n Display Unearned Mission Badges\n Assign Recognition Badges to Experience Cloud Site Members\n Delete Assigned Badges\n Use the API to Give Recognition Badges Sample Code\n Reputation Overview\n Share a Link to Your Experience Cloud Site\n Switch Between Your Salesforce Org and Your Experience Cloud Sites\n Use Reporting in Experience Cloud Sites\n Considerations\n\nYou are here:\n\nSALESFORCE HELP\nDOCS\nEXPERIENCE CLOUD\nMissions\n\nGame mechanics, such as using badges, are a great way to get your users involved in your Experience Cloud site. However, assigning badges manually can be time consuming. Instead, use the Missions feature to assign members badges automatically. Community managers have their say in what action earns a badge and when it can be awarded, and then Missions takes care of the rest. And members can see which badges they haven’t yet earned, inspiring action.\n\nREQUIRED EDITIONS\nAvailable in: Enterprise, Professional, Unlimited, and Developer editions.\n\nCommunity managers create missions and choose the badge, the action, and the threshold. For example, a mission could assign the Nice Work badge when a member answers 10 questions. Actions you can choose from include writing a post or comment, receiving a like, and more. Members can earn each mission badge once.\n\nNOTE Badges can only be assigned to users and by users who have Chatter enabled.\nCreate a Mission\nCreate a mission, choosing an action, threshold, and badge, to automatically give badges to your members.\nDisplay Unearned Mission Badges\nInspire members to participate more in your Experience Cloud site by showing them the badges they can earn. You can display the unearned badges in the member’s recognition badges list.\nDID THIS ARTICLE SOLVE YOUR ISSUE?\nLet us know so we can improve!\nYes\nNo\n ",
